---
/**
 * E-E-A-T Trust & Credentials section
 * Shows professional credentials, insurance, memberships
 */
---

<section class="content-section bg-white trust-credentials-section">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why Trust Bullard Locks</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Professional credentials, verified and up to date.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trust-grid">
      <div class="trust-card">
        <div class="trust-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-id-badge"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="trust-label">Licensed & Registered</h3>
        <p class="trust-detail">MLA (Master Locksmiths Association) member. CRB/DBS enhanced disclosure checked. Registered with the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO) for data protection compliance.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-card">
        <div class="trust-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="trust-label">Metropolitan Police Approved</h3>
        <p class="trust-detail">Listed on the Metropolitan Police approved locksmith contractor scheme - one of the most rigorous vetting processes for locksmiths operating in London.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-card">
        <div class="trust-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-file-contract"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="trust-label">Fully Insured</h3>
        <p class="trust-detail">Comprehensive public liability insurance covering all locksmith, auto locksmith and safe engineering work. Certificate available on request for commercial clients.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-card">
        <div class="trust-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="trust-label">30+ Years in Business</h3>
        <p class="trust-detail">William Bullard has been a practising locksmith since the early 1990s. Over three decades of hands-on experience across residential, commercial and automotive locksmithing.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-card">
        <div class="trust-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="trust-label">5-Star Google Rating</h3>
        <p class="trust-detail">Consistently rated 5.0 stars on Google by verified customers. Every review is from a genuine client - no incentivised or fake reviews.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-card">
        <div class="trust-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-tools"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="trust-label">British Standard Locks</h3>
        <p class="trust-detail">All replacement locks meet or exceed BS3621 and TS007 standards, satisfying insurance requirements. We fit anti-snap, anti-bump and anti-pick cylinders as standard.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .trust-credentials-section {
    padding-top: 80px;
    padding-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .trust-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .trust-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-light, #f8fafa);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(14, 74, 77, 0.08);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .trust-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(14, 74, 77, 0.08);
  }

  .trust-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent), #159585);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .trust-label {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-main);
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }

  .trust-detail {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .trust-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .trust-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .trust-credentials-section {
      padding-top: 56px;
      padding-bottom: 56px;
    }
  }
</style>
